info.pavie.opennetworkmap.controller.converter

Interface NetworkConverter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GridConverter, IntervalConverter

    public interface NetworkConverter
    A network converter will convert a Network into a RepresentableNetwork. This allows to create representations of given network (to export them later).

    • Method Summary
